Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:38.32,jpop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Your tear change real my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.47,0:02:47.36,jpop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}流れる大気から 世界を揺らす
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:52.46,jpop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}タイムリミットは もう近いよ どうする?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.76,0:02:57.22,jpop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Shout! 深い漆黒の眼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.04,0:03:02.50,jpop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Ah 消えない遺恨を背負うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.86,0:03:07.73,jpop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}はばたく闇の勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:10.13,jpop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}掻き立てる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.36,0:03:11.52,jpop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Change the world
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:12.70,jpop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Strong my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:15.40,jpop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}支配されても突き刺す
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.52,0:03:17.94,jpop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}賞賛は報酬で
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:20.87,jpop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}火照る美学鳴らす
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.12,0:03:26.65,jpop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}涙は見せないで 今はまだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:30.79,jpop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}譲ると誓うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.12,0:03:36.33,jpop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}解き放て REALIZE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.30,0:02:32.89,cnop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}{\an8}我啊… 将会改变整个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:38.32,cnop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}{\an8}你的泪水牵动了我真实的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.47,0:02:47.36,cnop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}{\an8}于澎湃大气之中 震撼着世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:52.46,cnop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}{\an8}时限就快到了 该如何是好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.76,0:02:57.22,cnop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}{\an8}呼喊吧! 深邃的乌黑之眼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.04,0:03:02.50,cnop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}{\an8}啊 背负着无法消去的遗恨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.86,0:03:07.73,cnop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}{\an8}大显身手的黑暗勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:10.13,cnop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}{\an8}崛地而起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.36,0:03:11.52,cnop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}{\an8}改变世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:12.70,cnop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}{\an8}强化心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:15.40,cnop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}{\an8}就算遭到支配也要全力一击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.52,0:03:17.94,cnop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}{\an8}以赞赏作为报酬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:20.87,cnop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}{\an8}响起那令人热血的美学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.12,0:03:26.65,cnop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}{\an8}现在还不是让我看到你的泪水之时…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:30.79,cnop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}{\an8}我发誓会守护着你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.12,0:03:36.33,cnop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}{\an8}不顾一切地来实现
Comment: 0,0:21:39.73,0:21:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.81,0:22:00.84,jped,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}愛のせいで眠れないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.34,0:22:06.21,jped,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}そっぽ向いて眠れないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.27,0:22:11.91,jped,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}どんな風に始まるんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.78,0:22:17.95,jped,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}なんで声がかすれるのさ?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.57,0:22:24.04,jped,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}とまらない 胸騒ぎのdream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.04,0:22:29.02,jped,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}囓った指が熱い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.69,0:22:37.95,jped,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}迷うよ、怖いよ、駄目だよ…スキダヨ!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.95,0:22:40.59,jped,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}my story あるstory
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.72,0:22:49.25,jped,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}お伽噺で寝かしつけるほど子どもじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.25,0:22:52.18,jped,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}my story あるstory
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.18,0:23:02.62,jped,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}キミのことだけ 考える日々じゃ苦しくなりそう
